{"word":"ἐπινέω","slug":"ἐπινέω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἐπινέω1</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:νέω'><el>νέω2</el></a>\n<el>(<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>-νήσω</el>,) </el><p/><i>to allot by spinning</i>, of the Fates, <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b><p/> <hr/> <el><b>ἐπινέω2</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:νέω'><el>νέω3</el></a>\n<p/><i>to heap up</i> or <i>load with</i> a thing, <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:genitive'>gen.</a>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b><p/> <hr/> <el><b>ἐπινέω3</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:νέω'><el>νέω1</el></a>\n<p/><i>to float on the top</i>.<p/>"}]}